[ACTIVITY] 訂單確認後決策出貨方式並並行包裝與通知
[ACTOR] 買家 -> {specs/actors/買家.md}
[ACTOR] 系統 -> {specs/actors/系統.md}
[ACTOR] 倉庫 -> {specs/actors/倉庫.md}

[INITIAL]
[STEP:1] @買家 {specs/features/C01-訂單/001-確認訂單.dsl.feature}
[DECISION:1a] 選擇出貨方式
  [BRANCH:1a:宅配]
    [STEP:1a.1] @系統 {specs/commands/建立宅配運單.feature}
  [BRANCH:1a:超商]
    [STEP:1a.2] @系統 {specs/commands/建立超商取貨單.feature}
[MERGE:1a]
[STEP:2] @系統 {specs/commands/鎖定出貨資訊.feature}
[FORK:2a]
  [PARALLEL:2a]
    [STEP:2a.1] @倉庫 {specs/commands/包裝商品.feature}
  [PARALLEL:2a]
    [STEP:2a.2] @系統 {specs/commands/發送出貨通知.feature}
[JOIN:2a]
[STEP:3] @系統 {specs/commands/更新訂單為已出貨.feature}
[FINAL]
